result.adr_address: 66號 Woosung St, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.name: Kam Shan Seafood Restaurant

reviews.text:
To be honest the food here is very very nice. Besides that, the waiter here very nice also.
It is a good experience to eat here.
Excellent local secret, but bring a local. No English and cash only!

This is an authentic Cantonese seafood experience located in a building at the corner of Austin street and Nathan road. This place can get very noisy but the food is worth it. Price wise, it's not expensive considering the food quality. This place can get pretty packed so either come here earlier or queue up.

Recently remodeled two weeks ago as of 05/23/2018. Quality of food continues to decline. Expect lines unless reservation is made ahead of time. It is fine for what it is but the quality is no longer what it was years ago.
Nice food and service

result.adr_address: 香港佐敦吳松街66號
result.name: 金山海鮮酒家

reviews.text: 食到懷舊雞蛋蒸魚腸👍👍👍
豬肺湯很好，濃味但又不咸，喝後沒有口渴感覺，真材實料
リーズナブルな価格で海鮮を楽しめるといった口コミが多いので訪れてみましたが、生簀の魚介類は全て時価。聞いてみたら、蟹(幅12〜3cm)が300ドル！約4200円！シャコはもっと高く、生簀の海鮮は諦め店内のメニューにある物とビールにしました。店内メニューは生簀程ではありませんが、普通の値段でみなさんが投稿している程安い店ではありませんよ。

To be honest the food here is very very nice. Besides that, the waiter here very nice also.
It is a good experience to eat here.
此餐廳海鮮雖然唔平但十分新鮮，亦煮得有水準!但是，此餐廳允許有些文明的客人吸煙。此做法但犯法仲對其他客人造成滋擾，非常之差，非常之健康，所以我會選擇唔再去，也建議其他人唔好去，因為香港海鮮好食嘅地方多得是 唔需要去吸二手煙，傷害自己的健康。
